    <title type="html"><![CDATA[使用Octopress教程大合集]]></title>
    <link href="http://Fatman13.github.io/blog/2013/06/24/shi-yong-octopressjiao-cheng-da-he-ji/"/>
    <updated>2013-06-24T12:11:00-07:00</updated>
